author: djames
msg: Fix a memory leak in make_baton by borrowing a reference to 'editor'.
* subversion/bindings/swig/python/libsvn_swig_py/swigutil_py.c
(make_baton): To avoid memory leaks, borrow the caller's reference to
'editor'.
(close_baton, close_file): Don't decrement the reference count of 'editor',
because it is now a borrowed reference.
Notes: Fixes a memory leak in the Python bindings reported by users of Trac.
See issue 2620. http://projects.edgewall.com/trac/ticket/2620
